## **ðŸ”¹ Edge Cases:**

(s1.length == s2.length()) 

**ðŸ”¹ Code:**

```java
java
CopyEdit
// Your Java solution here
class Solution {
    // Function is to check whether two strings are anagram of each other or not.
    public static boolean areAnagrams(String s1, String s2) {

        // Your code here
        int n = s1.length();
        int m = s2.length();
        if(n != m){
            return false;
        }
        int []freq = new int[26];
        // 26 alphabet
        for(int i = 0; i<n; i++){
            freq[s1.charAt(i) - 'a']++;
            freq[s2.charAt(i) - 'a']--;
        }
        for(int count : freq){
            if(count != 0) return false;
        }
        return true;
    }
}

```

